  <entry>
    <title>如何更新博客内容</title>
    <url>/2025/08/27/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="📚-Hexo博客内容更新指南"><a href="#📚-Hexo博客内容更新指南" class="headerlink" title="📚 Hexo博客内容更新指南"></a>📚 Hexo博客内容更新指南</h1><p>欢迎学习如何在你的Hexo博客中添加和更新内容！</p>
<h2 id="🎯-创建新文章的方法"><a href="#🎯-创建新文章的方法" class="headerlink" title="🎯 创建新文章的方法"></a>🎯 创建新文章的方法</h2><h3 id="方法一：使用Hexo命令（推荐）"><a href="#方法一：使用Hexo命令（推荐）" class="headerlink" title="方法一：使用Hexo命令（推荐）"></a>方法一：使用Hexo命令（推荐）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新文章</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new <span class="string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新页面</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new page <span class="string">&quot;页面名称&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建草稿</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new draft <span class="string">&quot;草稿标题&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="方法二：手动创建"><a href="#方法二：手动创建" class="headerlink" title="方法二：手动创建"></a>方法二：手动创建</h3><p>直接在 <code>source/_posts/</code> 目录下创建 <code>.md</code> 文件</p>
<h2 id="📝-文章Front-Matter配置"><a href="#📝-文章Front-Matter配置" class="headerlink" title="📝 文章Front Matter配置"></a>📝 文章Front Matter配置</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章标题</span>                    <span class="comment"># 必需</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2025-08-27 10:00:00</span>         <span class="comment"># 发布日期</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">updated:</span> <span class="number">2025-08-27 12:00:00</span>      <span class="comment"># 更新日期（可选）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span>                             <span class="comment"># 标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签1</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span>                       <span class="comment"># 分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">主分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">子分类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cover:</span> <span class="string">图片URL</span>                     <span class="comment"># 封面图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">文章描述</span>              <span class="comment"># 文章摘要</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>                         <span class="comment"># 置顶（可选）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="🔄-更新流程"><a href="#🔄-更新流程" class="headerlink" title="🔄 更新流程"></a>🔄 更新流程</h2><h3 id="1-编辑内容"><a href="#1-编辑内容" class="headerlink" title="1. 编辑内容"></a>1. 编辑内容</h3><ul>
<li>修改现有文章或创建新文章</li>
<li>使用Markdown语法编写内容</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="2-本地预览"><a href="#2-本地预览" class="headerlink" title="2. 本地预览"></a>2. 本地预览</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动本地服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-访问预览"><a href="#3-访问预览" class="headerlink" title="3. 访问预览"></a>3. 访问预览</h3><p>打开浏览器访问：<code>http://localhost:4000</code></p>
<h2 id="💡-实用技巧"><a href="#💡-实用技巧" class="headerlink" title="💡 实用技巧"></a>💡 实用技巧</h2><h3 id="Butterfly主题特殊语法"><a href="#Butterfly主题特殊语法" class="headerlink" title="Butterfly主题特殊语法"></a>Butterfly主题特殊语法</h3><h4 id="提示框"><a href="#提示框" class="headerlink" title="提示框"></a>提示框</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">成功提示</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note info %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">信息提示</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note warning %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">警告提示</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note danger %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">危险提示</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="按钮"><a href="#按钮" class="headerlink" title="按钮"></a>按钮</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% btn &#x27;URL&#x27;, 按钮文字, 图标, 颜色 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="标签页"><a href="#标签页" class="headerlink" title="标签页"></a>标签页</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs 标签页名称 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab 标签1 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">内容1</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab 标签2 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">内容2</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="📊-内容管理建议"><a href="#📊-内容管理建议" class="headerlink" title="📊 内容管理建议"></a>📊 内容管理建议</h2><ol>
<li><strong>定期备份</strong>：定期备份 <code>source</code> 目录</li>
<li><strong>图片管理</strong>：建议使用图床服务存储图片</li>
<li><strong>SEO优化</strong>：合理设置标题、描述和标签</li>
<li><strong>分类规划</strong>：建立清晰的分类体系</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="🚀-部署更新"><a href="#🚀-部署更新" class="headerlink" title="🚀 部署更新"></a>🚀 部署更新</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成并部署</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo generate --deploy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或分步执行</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">npx hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<p>现在你已经掌握了更新博客内容的方法！开始创作你的精彩文章吧！ 🎉</p>
]]></content>
